Boston Common Funds
Boston Common Funds invest in U.S. and International markets with a focus on sustainability and responsibility. At Boston Common, we use our voice as the funds' manager on behalf of shareholders to raise sustainability issues with select portfolio companies to encourage transparency and accountability. We seek companies for investment that we believe have visionary management teams that take innovative approaches to the challenges their industries, society, and the world as a whole face.



